#: ../../E/Easter-egging.rst:9
msgid ""
"[IBM] The act of replacing unrelated components more or less at random in "
"hopes that a malfunction will go away. Hackers consider this the normal "
"operating mode of :ref:`field-circus` techs and do not love them for it. See"
" also the jokes under :ref:`field-circus`\\. Compare :ref:`shotgun-"
"debugging`\\."
msgstr ""
"[IBM] 故障が消えてくれることを期待して、無関係な部品を多かれ少なかれ手当たり次第に交換する行為。ハッカーはこれを\\ :ref:`field-"
"circus`\\ の技術者の通常の動作モードとみなし、そのことで彼らを好きにはなれない。\\ :ref:`field-circus`\\ "
"の項のジョークも参照。\\ :ref:`shotgun-debugging`\\ と比較せよ。"
